[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":162},["Reactive",2],{"content-query-gkztW4N7SE":3},{"_path":4,"_dir":5,"_draft":6,"_partial":6,"_locale":7,"title":8,"description":9,"director":10,"time":11,"types":12,"img":13,"info":14,"client":15,"body":16,"_type":157,"_id":158,"_source":159,"_file":160,"_extension":161},"/outher/ethereum-website-pr","outher",false,"","Ethereum website contribution","一次很好的人生体验，体验到了 CTT 的快递服务，以及 Ethereum community contribution 生态的完善。","ritsu","2025.02.19","cc","life/eth/1.png","https://ethereum.org/en/contributing/#contributors","Ethereum Foundation",{"type":17,"children":18,"toc":154},"root",[19],{"type":20,"tag":21,"props":22,"children":29},"element","main-content",{":client":23,":img":24,":info":25,":time":26,":title":27,":types":28},"client","img","info","time","title","types",[30,35,62,68,82,87,109,123,128,141],{"type":20,"tag":31,"props":32,"children":34},"text-sum",{":desc":33},"description",[],{"type":20,"tag":36,"props":37,"children":38},"p",{},[39,42,51,53,60],{"type":40,"value":41},"text","说实话当 isabella 告诉我能拿到 ethereum 的明信片和小周边物料还挺让我意外的。我以为会像 ",{"type":20,"tag":43,"props":44,"children":48},"a",{"href":45,"rel":46},"https://github.com/TylerAPfledderer",[47],"nofollow",[49],{"type":40,"value":50},"Tyler Pfledderer",{"type":40,"value":52}," 大佬那样高强度提 pr 才会收到。可以选择去 Devcon 现场领取或者邮寄，我没钱去泰国并且 English 也不怎么好所以选择了邮寄。体验到了 ",{"type":20,"tag":43,"props":54,"children":57},{"href":55,"rel":56},"https://www.ctt.pt/",[47],[58],{"type":40,"value":59},"CTT's",{"type":40,"value":61}," 没想到是从德国发出的。",{"type":20,"tag":63,"props":64,"children":67},"text-space",{"img":65,"info":66},"life/eth/2.jpg,life/eth/3.jpg,life/eth/4.jpg","图 1 ｜ 等了大约三个月的快递，让我意外的是过海关的时候竟然没被拦。",[],{"type":20,"tag":36,"props":69,"children":70},{},[71,73,80],{"type":40,"value":72},"不过也没什么好意外的，毕竟 ethereum website 的 designer 有一位是在奥地利的。",{"type":20,"tag":43,"props":74,"children":77},{"href":75,"rel":76},"https://github.com/nloureiro",[47],[78],{"type":40,"value":79},"Nuno Loureiro",{"type":40,"value":81}," 让我学到了很多在简洁、设计语言方面的靠量。我设计好自己的代表作字体后与他分享了，没想到还给我点了 Star，很高兴可以得到专业人士的肯定。",{"type":20,"tag":36,"props":83,"children":84},{},[85],{"type":40,"value":86},"我本来已经开始幻想拿到 be feature 了。没想到属实无望，不是很有创意，但能拿到 zccol 的编辑推荐也很开心了。以前我总是崇洋媚外的，但经过这次才让我发现国内的平台也是很鼓励新人的。",{"type":20,"tag":36,"props":88,"children":89},{},[90,92,99,101,107],{"type":40,"value":91},"我为 Ethereum website 水了差不多 6 个 PR，并且在 discord 中被标记成了 ",{"type":20,"tag":93,"props":94,"children":96},"code",{"className":95},[],[97],{"type":40,"value":98},"desing",{"type":40,"value":100}," 以及 ",{"type":20,"tag":93,"props":102,"children":104},{"className":103},[],[105],{"type":40,"value":106},"contributors",{"type":40,"value":108}," 在水 pr 的过程中我学习到了很多。比较让我记忆深刻的是 Ethereum website 的容错性比较高，project 非常的组件化。我提交了很多关于 i18n layout overflow 的 fix pr。因为我发现在 english 下可能 layout 没有问题，但在什么俄罗斯语、以及阿拉伯语的环境下，可能会导致 overflow 的问题。",{"type":20,"tag":36,"props":110,"children":111},{},[112,114,121],{"type":40,"value":113},"我并没有学习过 react，但是我还挺喜欢 react 做出的 website 的，可能组件库较多？一般用 react 的都会堆叠 gsap、three.js 可能对此支持的比较好，生态完善。而且 JSX、TSX 看起来也很不错。对于我来说很容易上手，让我学习到了 chakra 和 ShadCN。对 ",{"type":20,"tag":43,"props":115,"children":118},{"href":116,"rel":117},"https://github.com/wackerow",[47],[119],{"type":40,"value":120},"wackerow",{"type":40,"value":122}," 高强度 Reviewers 印象深刻。",{"type":20,"tag":36,"props":124,"children":125},{},[126],{"type":40,"value":127},"第一次提交 pr 发现就几十行 code 会有 designer、web front-end 一起 Reviewers，学到很多流程方面的。",{"type":20,"tag":36,"props":129,"children":130},{},[131,133,139],{"type":40,"value":132},"除了前端技术栈和设计之外，我还学习到了比较大的项目是如何运营的。Ethereum 做了很多类似游戏成就的生态，例如引入了 allcontributors、gitpoap、galxe 这些，比如完成了 5 pr 会给 galxe OAT 相当于一个 NFT 了相当于表示",{"type":20,"tag":134,"props":135,"children":136},"strong",{},[137],{"type":40,"value":138},"参与过、贡献过、出席过某个项目或事件",{"type":40,"value":140}," 不过也是要花很多时间去弄这些就对了。",{"type":20,"tag":36,"props":142,"children":143},{},[144,146,152],{"type":40,"value":145},"Ethereum 发的 galxe OAT 好像是 Layer 2 network 的东西，TEAM 确实很成熟。可以增加很多参与体验，以及体验之后的略微成就感。很多项目不会弄的这么好，弄的这么全，也难怪 Ethereum 的 community 人很多。可以从 ",{"type":20,"tag":43,"props":147,"children":149},{"href":14,"rel":148},[47],[150],{"type":40,"value":151},"contributors list",{"type":40,"value":153}," 就能看出。",{"title":7,"searchDepth":155,"depth":155,"links":156},2,[],"markdown","content:outher:ethereum-website-pr.md","content","outher/ethereum-website-pr.md","md",1752860616177]